1
00:00:00,004 --> 00:01:00,004
( Watch on www.kissasia.co, .club, .be, .org, .net, .id, .xyz )

2
00:01:02,258 --> 00:01:05,385
I can't get a single word in.

3
00:01:06,211 --> 00:01:09,150
