11
00:01:48,713 --> 00:01:50,214
Wait, are they kissing?

12
00:01:50,214 --> 00:01:52,025
A kiss.

13
00:01:52,025 --> 00:01:53,082
- Huh?
- What?

14
00:01:53,082 --> 00:01:55,272
What?

15
00:01:55,272 --> 00:01:58,258
Wait, right here?

16
00:01:58,258 --> 00:01:59,265
Are you insane?

17
00:01:59,265 --> 00:02:01,625
You just said we should kiss.

18
00:02:01,625 --> 00:02:04,795
- When did I say that?
- You literally just said it.

19
00:02:04,795 --> 00:02:07,315
Don't go.

20
00:02:09,358 --> 00:02:11,736
I told you not to go.

21
00:02:11,736 --> 00:02:14,947
Wait, you meant me?

22
00:02:14,947 --> 00:02:16,362
Seriously?

23
00:02:16,362 --> 00:02:19,160
You actually came all the way here to stop me?

24
00:02:19,160 --> 00:02:21,704
You like Korean food.

25
00:02:21,704 --> 00:02:25,416
Do not lose weight over there.

26
00:02:25,416 --> 00:02:27,418
Just stay here.

27
00:02:27,418 --> 00:02:29,837
Are you serious?

28
00:02:29,837 --> 00:02:31,499
This is not a prank, right?

29
00:02:31,499 --> 00:02:32,999
You cannot take it back later.

30
00:02:32,999 --> 00:02:37,128
If I were going to, I would not have run here.

31
00:02:37,128 --> 00:02:40,339
You even ran here.

32
00:02:40,339 --> 00:02:42,425
Ui Jeong...

33
00:02:42,425 --> 00:02:44,052
Are you crazy?

34
00:02:44,052 --> 00:02:45,511
What's the problem?

35
00:02:45,511 --> 00:02:46,771
Come here.

36
00:02:46,771 --> 00:02:51,193
It's been a while since we kissed.

37
00:02:51,942 --> 00:02:53,986
Do you want to die?

38
00:02:53,986 --> 00:02:55,897
Come here.

39
00:02:55,897 --> 00:02:57,023
Ui Jeong!

40
00:02:57,023 --> 00:02:58,399
You...

41
00:02:58,399 --> 00:03:02,119
If I catch you today, I'm kissing you.

42
00:03:02,119 --> 00:03:04,622
Tae Hyung.

43
00:03:06,829 --> 00:03:10,189
You are really not going to the U.S., right?

44
00:03:13,112 --> 00:03:14,340
Yeah.

45
00:03:14,340 --> 00:03:15,708
I'm not going.

46
00:03:15,708 --> 00:03:16,793
And this...

47
00:03:16,793 --> 00:03:20,179
Excuse me, lovebirds.

48
00:03:20,179 --> 00:03:21,863
Sorry to interrupt,

49
00:03:21,863 --> 00:03:22,882
but

50
00:03:22,882 --> 00:03:24,772
I just need to grab my bag.

51
00:03:24,772 --> 00:03:27,225
You can go ahead.

52
00:03:27,225 --> 00:03:29,631
Sun Tae Hyung.

53
00:03:34,107 --> 00:03:36,794
I'm not going.

54
00:03:46,949 --> 00:03:48,958
So did Mr. Gyu Jeong say that

55
00:03:48,958 --> 00:03:52,044
without even knowing the whole story?

56
00:03:52,044 --> 00:03:54,589
Seriously...

57
00:03:56,132 --> 00:03:58,676
Well, still...

58
00:03:58,676 --> 00:04:03,389
Thanks to that, I got to see you like this.

59
00:04:09,044 --> 00:04:11,542
Thanks for coming to me.

60
00:04:11,542 --> 00:04:14,984
But even if you had not,

61
00:04:14,984 --> 00:04:18,676
I would have come to you.

62
00:04:18,676 --> 00:04:21,560
Really?

63
00:04:21,560 --> 00:04:25,399
Leaving Woo Joo and me behind,
weren't you doing just fine in your new place?

64
00:04:25,399 --> 00:04:29,659
I nearly got sick trying to hold back
how much I missed you.

65
00:04:32,531 --> 00:04:35,160
You know,

66
00:04:36,133 --> 00:04:38,889
I used to be someone who thought nothing of

67
00:04:38,889 --> 00:04:42,045
coming home to a dark, empty house.

68
00:04:42,045 --> 00:04:46,551
But after meeting you and Woo Joo,

69
00:04:46,551 --> 00:04:49,810
that quiet silence

70
00:04:49,810 --> 00:04:53,370
started to feel unbearably lonely.

71
00:04:58,769 --> 00:05:02,329
Even Woo Joo whining,

72
00:05:08,253 --> 00:05:10,530
and all those little everyday moments

73
00:05:10,530 --> 00:05:11,832
we used to share...

74
00:05:11,832 --> 00:05:15,309
Once they were gone,

75
00:05:15,309 --> 00:05:19,030
the house didn't feel like home anymore.

76
00:05:20,869 --> 00:05:24,590
Without you and Woo Joo there,

77
00:05:26,055 --> 00:05:29,899
it felt unbearably lonely.

78
00:05:29,899 --> 00:05:32,625
Maybe...

79
00:05:32,625 --> 00:05:35,371
I don't think I can live
without you and Woo Joo anymore.

80
00:05:35,371 --> 00:05:36,795
Don't worry.

81
00:05:36,795 --> 00:05:39,352
We'll just stay together from now on.

82
00:05:39,352 --> 00:05:40,528
You better be ready.

83
00:05:40,528 --> 00:05:45,867
I'm going to stick right by your side
and chatter your ear off all day.

84
00:05:47,296 --> 00:05:49,664
I like that.

85
00:05:55,163 --> 00:05:57,276
Tae Hyung.

86
00:05:57,276 --> 00:06:00,295
Do you want some ramen?

87
00:06:02,643 --> 00:06:05,344
Ramen?

88
00:06:07,190 --> 00:06:09,327
Yeah.

89
00:06:10,558 --> 00:06:11,893
Tonight?

90
00:06:25,114 --> 00:06:26,399
Hyun Jin.

91
00:06:26,399 --> 00:06:28,234
Woo Joo's asleep now.

92
00:06:28,234 --> 00:06:29,412
Then we...

93
00:06:29,412 --> 00:06:31,104
Good work.

94
00:06:31,104 --> 00:06:32,989
You haven't eaten yet, right?

95
00:06:32,989 --> 00:06:35,700
I would cook you a proper meal if I could,

96
00:06:35,700 --> 00:06:38,127
but I just ran out of rice.

97
00:06:38,127 --> 00:06:40,254
Ramen?

98
00:06:43,674 --> 00:06:47,178
So you really meant just ramen.

99
00:06:48,462 --> 00:06:50,981
- Let's eat.
- Okay.

100
00:07:01,567 --> 00:07:03,500
What?

101
00:07:03,500 --> 00:07:04,847
Nothing.

102
00:07:04,847 --> 00:07:08,190
I just like looking at you.

103
00:07:08,190 --> 00:07:10,818
How can you say
something like that so casually?

104
00:07:10,818 --> 00:07:12,028
Why not?

105
00:07:12,028 --> 00:07:13,996
I'm not going anywhere this time.

106
00:07:13,996 --> 00:07:15,948
Why? Should I just turn around and leave again?

107
00:07:15,948 --> 00:07:17,174
No, no.

108
00:07:17,174 --> 00:07:19,001
It's just...

109
00:07:19,001 --> 00:07:22,621
being like this with you all of a sudden
feels a little awkward.

110
00:07:22,621 --> 00:07:24,923
Then get used to it.

111
00:07:24,923 --> 00:07:28,951
You know, I'm actually a pretty decent guy.

112
00:07:28,951 --> 00:07:31,526
Since when were you like this?

113
00:07:31,526 --> 00:07:32,715
Why?

114
00:07:32,715 --> 00:07:33,849
Come here.

115
00:07:33,849 --> 00:07:35,151
You don't like it?

116
00:07:35,151 --> 00:07:37,721
Who said I don't?

117
00:07:37,721 --> 00:07:40,064
Let go of my hand and eat your ramen.

118
00:07:40,064 --> 00:07:42,608
- Here.
- No.

119
00:07:43,404 --> 00:07:45,651
I'm kissing you instead.

120
00:07:45,651 --> 00:07:48,606
Hey, then how are you supposed to eat?

121
00:07:48,606 --> 00:07:49,615
Why not?

122
00:07:49,615 --> 00:07:51,442
We'll hold hands like this,

123
00:07:51,442 --> 00:07:52,701
and with the power of love,

124
00:07:52,701 --> 00:07:53,927
I'll eat with my left hand.

125
00:07:53,927 --> 00:07:55,639
- With your left hand?
- Yeah.

126
00:07:55,639 --> 00:07:56,864
Let's see.

127
00:07:56,864 --> 00:07:57,907
Eat.

128
00:07:57,907 --> 00:07:58,957
Hard, right?

129
00:07:58,957 --> 00:08:02,003
- See? I can do it.
- Hard, right?

130
00:08:04,677 --> 00:08:07,735
That's the power of love.

131
00:08:18,227 --> 00:08:20,403
[Episode 11]

132
00:08:50,884 --> 00:08:55,374
I'm sorry I left like that yesterday.

133
00:08:55,374 --> 00:08:59,316
Did something happen?

134
00:09:04,100 --> 00:09:05,766
I...

135
00:09:05,766 --> 00:09:08,489
did like you too.

136
00:09:08,489 --> 00:09:10,669
Past tense, huh?

137
00:09:10,669 --> 00:09:13,149
I think it's time I gave you my answer

138
00:09:13,149 --> 00:09:16,642
to your confession.

139
00:09:18,956 --> 00:09:21,198
Yoon Seong.

140
00:09:21,198 --> 00:09:24,541
There's someone I like.

141
00:09:31,073 --> 00:09:34,106
It's Sun Tae Hyung, isn't it?

142
00:09:37,142 --> 00:09:39,175
I'm sorry.

143
00:09:39,175 --> 00:09:41,218
Honestly...

144
00:09:41,218 --> 00:09:43,554
I kind of expected it.

145
00:09:43,554 --> 00:09:45,848
You might not realize it,

146
00:09:45,848 --> 00:09:48,309
