148
00:09:51,782 --> 00:09:53,647
Still... I'm relieved.

149
00:09:53,647 --> 00:09:56,734
That it's Sun Tae Hyung.

150
00:09:56,734 --> 00:09:58,569
I could tell

151
00:09:58,569 --> 00:10:02,364
he truly cares about you
and Woo Joo like family.

152
00:10:02,364 --> 00:10:06,870
It feels like you've found someone
who can really become your family.

153
00:10:07,870 --> 00:10:10,530
I'm really glad.

154
00:10:20,579 --> 00:10:22,384
I'll head this way.

155
00:10:22,384 --> 00:10:25,586
Get home safe.

156
00:10:29,444 --> 00:10:31,185
Hyun Jin.

157
00:10:31,185 --> 00:10:32,937
Yes?

158
00:10:32,937 --> 00:10:34,730
Actually, that day...

159
00:10:34,730 --> 00:10:37,438
Sun Tae Hyung was there too.

160
00:10:37,438 --> 00:10:39,735
The day of Woo Joo's daycare recital.

161
00:10:39,735 --> 00:10:43,558
I should've told you right away.

162
00:10:43,558 --> 00:10:45,939
But I couldn't,

163
00:10:46,659 --> 00:10:50,257
because I thought you might fall for him.

164
00:10:50,257 --> 00:10:52,873
For now,

165
00:10:52,873 --> 00:10:56,979
it might be hard for me
to completely sort out my feelings,

166
00:10:57,670 --> 00:11:01,123
but I still hope you're happy.

167
00:11:03,166 --> 00:11:05,685
I mean that.

168
00:11:15,020 --> 00:11:18,253
Okay, go play.

169
00:11:19,032 --> 00:11:22,611
Woo Joo, go play. It's your favorite slide.

170
00:11:22,611 --> 00:11:25,322
No.

171
00:11:25,322 --> 00:11:27,575
Why? Then should we go back inside?

172
00:11:27,575 --> 00:11:28,826
No.

173
00:11:28,826 --> 00:11:31,579
Woo Joo, you can't say no to everything.

174
00:11:31,579 --> 00:11:32,972
What do you like, then?

175
00:11:32,972 --> 00:11:36,052
I like Uncle.

176
00:11:37,084 --> 00:11:38,383
What did you say, Woo Joo?

177
00:11:38,383 --> 00:11:42,056
I like Uncle.

178
00:11:44,600 --> 00:11:47,219
That's right, I'm your uncle.

179
00:11:47,219 --> 00:11:50,022
Woo Joo, say it again. You like your uncle?

180
00:11:50,022 --> 00:11:52,900
I like Uncle.

181
00:11:53,984 --> 00:11:56,570
I like you a lot too, Woo Joo.

182
00:11:56,570 --> 00:11:58,272
You're the cutest.

183
00:11:58,272 --> 00:11:59,982
Come on, let's go play.

184
00:11:59,982 --> 00:12:01,191
Give me your hand.

185
00:12:01,191 --> 00:12:03,405
Let's go.

186
00:12:04,661 --> 00:12:06,196
Woo Joo.

187
00:12:06,196 --> 00:12:09,296
Woo Joo!

188
00:12:14,955 --> 00:12:18,500
Hey, Woo Joo. You just said you liked me.

189
00:12:18,500 --> 00:12:19,877
I just got here.

190
00:12:19,877 --> 00:12:21,670
Let's play with Auntie.

191
00:12:21,670 --> 00:12:22,756
Climb up.

192
00:12:22,756 --> 00:12:26,334
One, two, three!

193
00:12:26,334 --> 00:12:29,821
- Jump, jump!
- Nice.

194
00:12:31,755 --> 00:12:33,599
By the way...

195
00:12:33,599 --> 00:12:36,953
Did you come to Woo Joo's daycare recital?

196
00:12:51,418 --> 00:12:52,993
Back then...

197
00:12:52,993 --> 00:12:56,287
I just didn't have the confidence.

198
00:12:56,287 --> 00:12:59,249
Whether I could really be

199
00:12:59,249 --> 00:13:03,170
a good family for you and Woo Joo.

200
00:13:03,170 --> 00:13:06,048
Or whether I even deserved it.

201
00:13:06,048 --> 00:13:09,190
That's what I kept thinking.

202
00:13:10,828 --> 00:13:12,388
Tae Hyung.

203
00:13:12,388 --> 00:13:15,265
I actually have pretty high standards.

204
00:13:15,265 --> 00:13:17,851
Where did that come from?

205
00:13:17,851 --> 00:13:20,171
It means I don't date just anyone.

206
00:13:20,171 --> 00:13:21,271
So,

207
00:13:21,271 --> 00:13:22,990
if you start thinking like that again,

208
00:13:22,990 --> 00:13:24,912
try believing in me,
the one who believes in you.

209
00:13:24,912 --> 00:13:26,817
Okay?

210
00:13:26,817 --> 00:13:28,612
You're right.

211
00:13:28,612 --> 00:13:30,674
We're really dating now.

212
00:13:31,376 --> 00:13:34,410
You just said it.

213
00:13:34,410 --> 00:13:36,837
So does that mean yesterday was our first day?

214
00:13:36,837 --> 00:13:38,997
And I'm your boyfriend now?

215
00:13:38,997 --> 00:13:41,184
Do you really have to say it out loud?

216
00:13:42,418 --> 00:13:45,212
Look at my girlfriend blushing.

217
00:13:45,212 --> 00:13:47,089
You're way too cute.

218
00:13:47,089 --> 00:13:48,465
Keep it down, will you?

219
00:13:48,465 --> 00:13:49,998
It's not like anyone's listening.

220
00:13:49,998 --> 00:13:51,955
I could say something even bigger.

221
00:13:51,955 --> 00:13:53,554
Attention, everyone!

222
00:13:53,554 --> 00:13:57,680
People of the world!
My girlfriend is this adorable!

223
00:13:57,680 --> 00:14:01,009
Woo Hyun Jin is my girlfriend!

224
00:14:01,009 --> 00:14:02,098
Seriously...

225
00:14:02,098 --> 00:14:04,324
Let's go.

226
00:14:12,467 --> 00:14:15,659
That's really great, right?

227
00:14:15,659 --> 00:14:17,327
Yeah, it really is.

228
00:14:17,327 --> 00:14:18,920
Good for them.

229
00:14:18,920 --> 00:14:21,148
- Let's give them a round of applause.
- Everyone, clap!

230
00:14:21,148 --> 00:14:23,791
Come on, clap!

231
00:14:25,804 --> 00:14:27,596
Everyone, clap!

232
00:14:27,596 --> 00:14:30,614
Congratulations.

233
00:14:30,614 --> 00:14:34,079
I told you not to do that.

234
00:14:34,079 --> 00:14:35,253
Thank you.

235
00:14:35,253 --> 00:14:36,388
Bring Woo Joo with you.

236
00:14:36,388 --> 00:14:38,791
Hey, wait up!

237
00:14:38,791 --> 00:14:42,026
Hey, my girlfriend! Wait!

238
00:14:49,034 --> 00:14:52,163
They're making a scene.

239
00:14:53,413 --> 00:14:55,916
I'm so embarrassed to live
in this neighborhood.

240
00:14:55,916 --> 00:14:59,244
Then why would you act like that in public?

241
00:14:59,244 --> 00:15:02,130
How was I supposed to know

242
00:15:02,130 --> 00:15:04,541
people would show up right then?

243
00:15:04,541 --> 00:15:06,919
But now that I think about it...

244
00:15:06,919 --> 00:15:08,670
You weren't trying

245
00:15:08,670 --> 00:15:12,229
to keep us a secret, were you?

246
00:15:12,229 --> 00:15:13,376
No.

247
00:15:13,376 --> 00:15:14,559
I was going to tell people.

248
00:15:14,559 --> 00:15:16,595
Just... in a more natural way.

249
00:15:16,595 --> 00:15:17,604
You know,

250
00:15:17,604 --> 00:15:19,920
